Gene Expression dataframe of RNA-Seq.

Source: R/gene_exp.R
gene_exp.Rd

Gene Expression dataframe of RNA-Seq.

Usage

data(gene_exp)

Format

Dataframe: gene expression dataframe with cols (samples) and rows (genes).

References

https://github.com/BioSciTools/BioSciToolsDatasets/tree/main/CorPlot/

Author

benben-miao

Examples

# 1. Library TOmicsVis package
library(TOmicsVis)

# 2. Load example dataset gene_exp
data(gene_exp)

# 3. View gene_exp
gene_exp
